  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个AWS架构图，展示客户端通过Cognito认证后访问API Gateway的完整流程。核心模块分成三块：认证层、API层，还有外部的客户端。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AWS Cloud",
        "Authentication",
        "API Layer",
        "Client",
        "Cognito",
        "APIGW"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。认证层里面，Cognito和User Pool的关系是包含还是连接？我理解为User Pool是Cognito的一个具体实例？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Cognito",
        "User Pool"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，用实线连接就行，表示Cognito服务关联到具体的User Pool。API层那边需要三个节点：API Gateway、Cognito Authorizer，还有Lambda函数。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Cognito",
        "User Pool",
        "APIGW",
        "Auth",
        "Lambda"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，API层已经画好了，APIGW连到Authorizer，Authorizer再连到Lambda。现在有个问题：User Pool和Authorizer之间需要体现验证关系吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "UserPool",
        "Auth",
        "Lambda",
        "APIGW"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "需要，这是关键。用虚线表示，标注'Validates tokens'，说明Authorizer会去验证User Pool颁发的token。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "UserPool",
        "Auth"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "虚线关系已加上。接下来画客户端流程？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "UserPool",
        "Auth"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "客户端用Postman来演示。流程分四步：第一步Postman向Cognito发起认证请求，第二步Cognito返回JWT Token，第三步Postman带Token调API Gateway，第四步APIGW返回响应。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Postman",
        "Cognito",
        "APIGW"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "四步流程都画好了，每条线都标了序号。最后需要给各个区域上色区分吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Postman",
        "Cognito",
